title: 159: NFL Draft player comparisons
itunes:title: 159: NFL Draft player comparisons
description:
In scouting meetings and the war room, teams are constantly making comparisons to see which NCAA players remind them of certain pros. Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks make their pro comparisons to the current crop of college prospects.
